text: “xallxh di thrng khu wi kæ brrda mu na fik chay læa brrda mu na fik hying læa phu ptiseth sraththa thanghlay sung fi nrk yahannam doythi phwk khea ca xyu nı nan tlxd kal man pen sing thi phx pheiyng kæ phwk khea læw læa xallxh kdi thrng hı phwk khea hang kil cak khwam xendu metta khxng phraxngkh læa sahrab phwk khea nan khux kar lngthosʹ xan cirang yangyun”
